snippet.title: Bomberland 64 Trailer (Commodore 64 Homebrew)
snippet.description:
Trailer for the forthcoming Bomberland 64 by Samar Productions. Available soon from RGCD on physical Commodore 64 cartridge and as a downloadable rom image for emulators and devices such as the Ultimate 1541-II.

Bomberland 64 is NTSC/PAL/GS compatible, and even uses the additional processing power on the C128 to provide a smoother play experience. Don't have a joystick? No problem - Bomberland is even playable on keyboard, meaning that all you need to play the game is a C64, cartridge and TV.
